Class Set

  • java.lang.Object
    • Room
      • Set
  • public class Set
extends Room
    Represents a Set on the board of the game. There are 10 of these Sets, each with their own name, Card, and Parts that the Player can interact with. This is a child class of the Room class, as it represents a specific type of Room.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jamal Marri, Megan Theimer
    See Also:
    Room, Card
